        <li>While walking, <strong>if the dog "leaves" you</strong> then you'll immediately <span class="text-red">pop-and-turn</span>.</li>
        <li>While walking, <strong>if the dog is in position</strong> <span class="text-green">praise and reward</span>.</li>
